{
  "id": "RAW_fe51eef1",
  "title": "刚刚，Ant Design 6.0 正式发布！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==&mid=2247536331&idx=1&sn=3bb713db63ac8f771d89761b81106dd5",
  "date": "2025-11-22 10:48:00",
  "author": "前端充电宝",
  "siteName": "前端充电宝",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=75bbe630&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FEO58xpw5UMNZ5iawH098W0RibiavNPNcjm0qs3KweNlUGt67gW6sPedkOjDl8ToaYBWpILiboqqzX6fl7D38piaGPMw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;overflow:hidden;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'SF Pro Text', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"height: auto;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mia5zridhgf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100052682\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46574074074074073\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(240, 240, 240) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ac8f5eb8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMNZ5iawH098W0RibiavNPNcjm0g1h8QXtw65kcHTGOWx9I5bqvJ50KFqAcvvbZkewMq44RQhdEsPHGnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时，Ant Design X 同步发布 2.0 版本。作为 Ant Design 面向 AI 场景的组件库，新版本带来了更强大的交互与渲染能力。</span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 18 成为起步要求</span></h2>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">v6 开始不再支持 React 17，之前为了兼容老版本保留的那些逻辑也一起清理掉了。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span leaf=\"\">如果你的项目还停在 17，需要先把 React 升到 18，再考虑上 v6。</span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">样式体系全面切到 CSS 变量</span></h2>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是这次变化里最明显的一项。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span leaf=\"\">v6 开始用&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">纯 CSS 变量</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;来处理主题，不再依赖 Less 做动态样式。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">带来的变化比较直接：</span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">主题切换更流畅</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">和构建工具的配合更简单</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以借助&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">@ant-design/static-style-extract</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;做静态样式提取，减少运行时消耗</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">正式不再支持 IE</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你项目有一套自己的主题，升级后最好检查一下相关变量。</span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">组件结构更一致、语义化更强</span></h2>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不少组件的 DOM 结构做了微调，class 命名也更统一了。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">主要目的是提升可访问性和可定制性，让后续的样式迭代更容易。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一般使用不会受影响，但如果你对组件内部结构做过深度定制，最好对照一下。</span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">新增和增强的一些能力</span></h2>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然没有加入大批新组件，但补上了几个常用需求：</span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">新增 Masonry（瀑布流）布局</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">Drawer 支持拖拽</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">InputNumber 加了 spinner</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">Tooltip 支持平移滚动</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n       <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">弹层背景默认做了模糊处理</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">都是比较实用的优化，也没有破坏性变更。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mia5zhl01p70\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100052681\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3851851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(240, 240, 240) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=96c8ff36&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMNZ5iawH098W0RibiavNPNcjm0nPleolhUXu6icoeiblEwXKmkDATe7F8sFjH1NMJLJD9RM52WrZ2XuJnw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">清理废弃 API</span></h2>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前 v4 已废弃、v5 暂留的一些 API，这次基本都被移除了。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">升级过程中如果遇到报错，多半就是踩在这里。</span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">写在最后</span></h2>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整体来说，v6 更像是把 antd 的基础设施重新整理了一遍，让它更贴近 React 18 的生态，也更符合现在的前端结构和样式习惯。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你的项目在用 v5，升级压力不大，重点检查 React 版本和自定义主题即可。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Ant Design 6.0 正式发布，核心变化包括要求 React 18、全面切换 CSS 变量样式体系、组件结构优化以及新增实用功能，旨在提升可维护性和生态兼容性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Ant Design 6.0 正式发布，核心变化包括要求 React 18、全面切换 CSS 变量样式体系、组件结构优化以及新增实用功能，旨在提升可维护性和生态兼容性。",
  "summary": "文章宣布了 Ant Design 6.0 的正式发布，并同步介绍了面向 AI 场景的 Ant Design X 2.0 版本。Ant Design 6.0 的核心更新包括不再支持 React 17，将 React 18 作为最低要求，以及将样式体系全面切换至纯 CSS 变量，以实现更流畅的主题切换和简化构建工具配合。此外，文章还提到组件结构的一致性和语义化增强，清理了废弃 API，并新增了 Masonry 布局、Drawer 拖拽、InputNumber spinner 等实用功能。整体而言，v6 更侧重于底层基础设施的整理和升级，使其更贴近现代前端生态，对于 v5 用户升级压力不大，主要需关注 React 版本和自定义主题的适配。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Ant Design 6.0 要求 React 18，并全面采用 CSS 变量管理样式。",
      "explanation": "此举清理了旧版兼容逻辑，简化了主题切换和构建工具配合，并支持静态样式提取，提升了性能和开发效率，但用户需升级 React 版本并检查自定义主题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "组件结构优化提升可访问性和可定制性。",
      "explanation": "DOM 结构微调和 class 命名统一，旨在提高组件的可访问性和未来样式迭代的便利性，对深度定制的用户需要关注兼容性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "新增实用功能并清理废弃 API，优化用户体验。",
      "explanation": "引入 Masonry 布局、Drawer 拖拽等功能，同时移除旧版废弃 API，使得组件库功能更完善，代码更精简，但升级时可能遇到 API 报错。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "v6 开始用纯 CSS 变量来处理主题，不再依赖 Less 做动态样式。",
    "整体来说，v6 更像是把 antd 的基础设施重新整理了一遍，让它更贴近 React 18 的生态，也更符合现在的前端结构和样式习惯。",
    "如果你的项目在用 v5，升级压力不大，重点检查 React 版本和自定义主题即可。"
  ],
